com.microsoft.bingads.v10.bulk.entities

Class BulkCampaignRadiusTarget

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.bingads.v10.internal.bulk.BulkObject
      • com.microsoft.bingads.v10.bulk.entities.BulkEntity
        • com.microsoft.bingads.v10.internal.bulk.entities.MultiRecordBulkEntity
          • com.microsoft.bingads.v10.bulk.entities.BulkCampaignRadiusTarget

  • public class BulkCampaignRadiusTarget
extends MultiRecordBulkEntity
    Represents a radius target that is associated with a campaign. This class exposes the BulkRadiusTarget.setRadiusTarget(com.microsoft.bingads.v10.campaignmanagement.RadiusTarget) and BulkRadiusTarget.getRadiusTarget() methods that can be used to read and write fields of the Campaign Radius Target record in a bulk file.

    One BulkCampaignRadiusTarget exposes a read only list of BulkCampaignRadiusTargetBid. Each BulkCampaignRadiusTargetBid instance corresponds to one Campaign Radius Target record in the bulk file. If you upload a BulkCampaignRadiusTarget, then you are effectively replacing any existing bids for the corresponding radius target.

    For more information, see Campaign Radius Target at http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=620245.

    See Also:
    BulkServiceManager, BulkOperation, BulkFileReader, BulkFileWriter

      • getStatus

        public Status getStatus()
        Gets the status of the target.

        The value is Active if the target is available in the customer's shared library. The value is Deleted if the target is deleted from the customer's shared library, or should be deleted in a subsequent upload operation. Corresponds to the 'Status' field in the bulk file.
